data.text: Winja, Yaye Nyasaye e kinde manyisi chandruokna;
Panda ne chenro maricho mag joma richo,
Gidiro asere kama giponde mondo gichwogo ngʼama onge ketho;
Gijiwore ngʼato gi ngʼato kuom chenrogi maricho,
Gichano timo ne ji marach kagiwacho niya,
To Nyasaye biro bayogi gi aserni;
Obiro loko lewgi mi gogi gin giwegi
Joma kare mondo obed moil kuom Jehova Nyasaye
